heading_context: Apply for or renew a British passport if you're visiting the UK
chunks.html_content:
Apply online to:

  • renew an adult passport
  • renew your child’s passport
  • get your child’s first passport - if your child has never had a passport or only been included on yours
  • get your first adult passport

There are different ways to renew or replace your passport if you’re outside the UK.

heading_context: Apply for or renew a British passport if you're visiting the UK
chunks.html_content:
Check how long it will take to get a passport before you apply.

If you need a passport urgently, you can find out more about the Online Premium or 1 week Fast Track services.

If you apply while you’re in the UK, your passport can only be sent to a UK address.

Do not book travel until you get your passport.
